<p>Select an image to upload and the image will be added to the screenshot gallery. An image caption is not required but recommended.</p>
<form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
<label for="screenshot">Browse Screenshot File..</label>
<div class="war-input">
<input id="screenshot" type="file" size="30" name="image" />
</div>

<label for="caption">Image Caption</label>
<div class="war-input">
<input id="caption" type="text" name="caption" size="30" />
</div>

<input type="submit" name="add" value="" class="btn" />
</form>